xbrlcore.linkbase
Class PresentationLinkbaseElement

java.lang.Object
  xbrlcore.linkbase.PresentationLinkbaseElement
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class PresentationLinkbaseElement
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

For each Concept in a taxonomy which appears in the presentation linkbase, there is one corresponding PresentationLinkbaseElement. This class represents a concept within the presentation linkbase and contains additional information as for example all successors.

Author:
Daniel Hamm
